<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 18:53:37 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>FRIEDENAU T恤叠放</title><link>https://some.pics/6a48052cd651a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;两件V领T恤，一件蓝色一件白色，平铺在木质表面上，白色T恤部分叠在蓝色上衣上。两件上衣胸前都用大号白色或黑色艺术字体印着"FRIEDENAU"，右侧还有较小的文字和图形元素。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt='Two v-neck t-shirts, one blue and one white, are laid out on a wooden surface, with the white shirt partially overlapping the blue one. Both shirts have "FRIEDENAU" printed in large white or black stylized lettering across the chest, along with smaller text and a graphic element to the right.' height="5707" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/b30/6a48052cd651a.jpg" width="4280"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://b30.some.pics"&gt;@b30&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 18:53:37 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a47cca71cbef</link><description>&lt;p&gt;#FensterFreitag&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Part of an old wooden barn where the red paint has partially faded, with an uneven roof.  There is a small, oblong window in the wall. In front of it stands a young tree, the shadow of which is reflected in  the window pane. " height="1692" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/6a47cca71cbef.jpg" width="1082"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 14:52:30 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>为气邻居刷房</title><link>https://some.pics/6a47c954ed158</link><description>&lt;p&gt;女子为气邻居而粉刷房屋&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt='A picture of a white house with horizontal red stripes running top to bottom, next to a "normal" looking house' height="1080" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/mikee/6a47c954ed158.jpg" width="1620"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://mikee.some.pics"&gt;@mikee&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 14:38:15 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a47685f4caab</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这幅色彩缤纷的壁画位于第二街240号，由丹佛艺术家鲍比·马吉·洛佩兹为2025年梅肯壁画节创作。洛佩兹以其充满活力的自然灵感艺术作品闻名，他将漩涡般的色彩、野生动物和花卉细节融入大规模设计中，为周围空间注入了能量与生机。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Colorful mural of a rabbit covered in vibrant flowers and foliage, surrounded by wildflowers and tall grasses on the side of a downtown building." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a47685f4caab.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 07:44:35 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a472392b2395</link><description>&lt;p&gt;发现了一片巨树森林。然后，又发现了一个巨树森林的博物馆。多么巧合！

红杉国家公园真是太棒了。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="In the foreground a museum with sign saying Giant Forest Museum. In the background a whole bunch of trees that makes the museum look very small." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dcr/6a472392b2395.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dcr.some.pics"&gt;@dcr&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jul 2026 02:51:02 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>